<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Zing in chungleng va'n Pathien a pak ui,
 Pakcha'n le A lopina chuh a phuong ui;
 A thilsiem in Amah a chawian ui,
 Mihing mai lo chuh sinsak ngai a um puou.

[V2]
 Lei leh van mi'n le chawian hitiu,
 Amauhaw sangin I chingzawu hi;
 Khawvel chengcheng in sa khawm leule,
 Amah chawihatna la sa seng puo'n au.

[V3]
 2. Nicheng in Na phatna ka mu zing ui,
 Sun leh zan, phalbi leh chuklai a um sek;
 Hun a thak bangin kipahna I nei,
 Kumsawt in Angelte tawh zaila sa'i tiu.

[V4]
 3. Hetna leh chitna leh thilhih theihna'n,
 Mihing chengcheng in Amah pakcha khawm in;
 Ei dinga A bawl cheng I gen seng puou,
 Kumsawt in A lungsietna gen seng puoi tiu.</lyrics>
<title>PRAISES IN THE MORNING</title>
</song>